import statsmodels.api as sm

#No Lag day model
y = call_weather_weekday['Total Inbound Calls ']

# Add constant term to X (intercept)
X_Lag0= sm.add_constant(X_Lag0)

# Fit the linear regression model
model_Lag0 = sm.OLS(y, X_Lag0).fit()

# Print model summary
print(model_Lag0.summary())
